---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Focus from "../components/focus/Focus.astro";
---

<Layout title="Focus">
  <main>
    <Focus type="headline" title="DazDotDev Blog">
      Working with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank">Astro</a> to migrate
      from WordPress to embrace a lean, modern and performant framework to help me
      write, build and deploy faster.
    </Focus>

    <Focus type="highlight" title="SolidJS">
      Recent fascination with learning how streamlined the <a
        href="https://www.solidjs.com/"
        target="_blank"
      >
        SolidJS
      </a> developer experience is compaired to React. Starting to hack together
      some demos to gain confidence.
    </Focus>

    <Focus type="highlight" title="InstantDB">
      <a href="https://www.instantdb.com/" target="_blank">InstantDB</a> is really
      inspiring tech. Got a first proof-of-concept demo working. Enthusiastically
      exploring.
    </Focus>
  </main>
</Layout>
